  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your training and reflexes allow you to react swiftly to avoid an opponents' attacks.</em> <br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>Dex 13.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">You gain a +1 dodge bonus to your AC. A condition that makes you lose your Dex bonus to AC also makes you lose the benefits of this feat.</p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">You get a +4 dodge bonus to Armor Class against attacks of opportunity caused when you move out of or within a threatened area. A condition that makes you lose your Dexterity bonus to Armor Class (if any) also makes you lose dodge bonuses.</p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Dodge bonuses stack with each other, unlike most types of bonuses.</p>",
